sentences.english: An IUD is also known as an Inter-Uterine Device.

sentences.english: Results Severe PIH and postpartum hemorrhage were the major factors that led to MOF.
sentences.chinese: 結果導致MOF的主要因素爲重度妊高徵及產後出血。

sentences.english: Objective To analyze the levels of cell adhesion molecules on deciduas from patients with pregnancy induced hypertension.
sentences.chinese: 目的分析妊高徵患者蛻膜粘附分子表達的變化。

sentences.english: Therefore complementing calcium in midterm pregnancy can reduce the morbidity of hypertension of pregnancy.
sentences.chinese: 所以於妊娠中期補鈣可以降低妊高徵的發病率。

sentences.english: The incidence of PIH increased in GDM patients with hyperlipidemia.

sentences.english: So, disturbances of PAPP-A might be one of the causes of PIH.
sentences.chinese: 其水平異常可能是導致妊高徵的原因之一。

sentences.english: The incidence rate of pregnancy induced hypertension can be decreased by earlier period clinical intervention.
sentences.chinese: 妊高徵經早期臨牀干預後可以降低其發病率。

sentences.english: Objective To study the cause of decreased erythrocyte deformability and its relation to pregnancy induced hypertension(PIH).
sentences.chinese: 目的探討紅細胞膜脂質成分的變化與妊高徵的關係。

sentences.english: The pregnancy progressed normally for Karen. In, time the labor pains came.
sentences.chinese: 凱倫在娠妊期間一切正常，不久，分娩的陣痛開始了。

sentences.english: We discuss the etiology of the PIH in the following three parts.
sentences.chinese: 本研究分爲三部分對妊高徵的病因學進行探討。

sentences.english: Objective To study the mechanism of using Chinese medicine tarragon soup to prevent and cure pregnancy induced hypertension syndrome(PIM).
sentences.chinese: 目的探討運用中藥茵陳湯預防及治療妊高徵的機理。

sentences.english: Objective To study tarragon soup whether has the role to prevent and cure pregnancy induced hypertension syndrome(PIH).
sentences.chinese: 目的研究茵陳湯是否具有預防及治療妊高徵的作用。
